http://www.economist.com:80/issue/08-06-96/wb1.html 199.173.162.110 19970113163853 text/html 4375
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 16:35:08 GMT
