<html><head><title>The Economist: cover credit</title>
<img src="http://www.economist.com/econlogosmall.gif" width=78 height=39  alt="The Economist Logo"></td>

<td align=right valign=top>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<ol><br>
<h2><i>The Economist</i>&#160;: cover credit</h2>
<p>
May 25th 1996 - May 31st 1996
</p><p>
<img src="cov25-05-96.jpg" alt="The Economist cover image">
</p><p>
The image on this week's cover is:
</p><p>
New York Skyline: &#160;David W Hamilton/The Image Bank<br>Oxen Ploughing, Sri Lanka: &#160;Stuart Nicol/Katz Pictures
</p><p>All Rights Reserved</p>
