http://www.economist.com:80/issue/27-04-96/ld1.html 199.173.162.110 19970113170824 text/html 9422
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 17:04:37 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 08-Aug-96 14:04:00 GMT
Content-length: 9237
