http://www.economist.com:80/issue/13-04-96/sf1.html 199.173.162.110 19970113171834 text/html 19699
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 17:14:36 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 08-Aug-96 14:03:58 GMT
