<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/issue/23-03-96/ld1.html 199.173.162.110 19970113173148 text/html 7366
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 17:27:45 GMT
