<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/issue/09-03-96/wtw1.html 199.173.162.110 19970113174055 text/html 6162
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 17:37:06 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 08-Aug-96 14:03:58 GMT
Content-length: 5977
